# CLIP ChangeLog for app-admin/logrotate

*logrotate-3.8.1-r8 (12 Feb 2018)

  12 Feb 2018; Timothée Ravier <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +logrotate-3.8.1-r8.ebuild, -logrotate-3.8.1-r7.ebuild:
  RBump for linux-headers 4.4 rebuild.

*logrotate-3.8.1-r7 (10 Nov 2015)

  10 Nov 2015; Alain Ozanne <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +logrotate-3.8.1-r7.ebuild, -logrotate-3.8.1-r7.ebuild,
  files/logrotate-3.8.1-clip-flags.patch:
  Change the "ext2_fs.h" include path to match with the linux-headers update in
  3.14.
  Update the ebuild dependencies.

*logrotate-3.8.1-r7 (21 Oct 2014)

  21 Oct 2014; Hugo Chargois <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +logrotate-3.8.1-r7.ebuild, -logrotate-3.8.1-r6.ebuild,
  files/logrotate.skel:
  Add "rotate" variable which is still needed when "maxage" is used.

*logrotate-3.8.1-r6 (24 Dec 2013)

