*logrotate-3.8.1 (06 Jun 2012)

  06 Jun 2012; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  logrotate-3.8.1.ebuild, +files/logrotate.skel,
  +files/logrotate-3.8.1-clip-flags.patch,
  +files/logrotate.cron.clip:
  Initial overlay import. Add skeleton file to generate logrotate.conf
  on CLIP, add patch to make logrotate manage immutable/append-only flags
  itself, add verictl entry to give logrotate CAP_LINUX_IMMUTABLE
  when the caller has it in its inheritable mask.
